    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 10th Level, your Sensing Technique has achieved new heights.</p><p> You have learned to recognize chakra by feeling alone.</p><p> Any jutsu that would change a creatures form after you have sensed them with Sensing Technique, proves ineffective, as you recognize their chakra through the illusion.</p><p> Additionally, while you are using Sensing Technique, you can spend your action to learn what clan they are from, if any.</p><p> Weaker Bloodlines, such as latent are not noticed, as their chakra is too concentrated.</p><p></p>",
